&lt;h2>The Automatic Way&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="the-automatic-way">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#the-automatic-way" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Define your building configuration into &lt;code>.custom-gcl.yml&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Run the command &lt;code>golangci-lint custom&lt;/code> (or &lt;code>golangci-lint custom -v&lt;/code> to have logs).&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Define the plugin inside the &lt;code>linters.settings.custom&lt;/code> section with the type &lt;code>module&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Run the resulting custom binary of golangci-lint (&lt;code>./custom-gcl&lt;/code> by default).&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Requirements:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Go&lt;/li>
&lt;li>git&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
