&lt;li>Add a blank-import of your module inside &lt;code>cmd/golangci-lint/plugins.go&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Run &lt;code>go mod tidy&lt;/code> (the module containing the plugin will be imported).&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Run &lt;code>make build&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Define the plugin inside the &lt;code>linters.settings.custom&lt;/code> section with the type &lt;code>module&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Run your custom version of golangci-lint.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
